Note: PUBLIC API
Note: ===================================================================

@Reasoning:
Snake-case public alias for create_hcl_parser, matching the naming
convention expected by the universal translation dispatcher. The
dispatcher uses underscore-prefixed module names and uniform
snake_case operations across all frontends.
@End Reasoning
Process called "hcl_parser_create" takes tokens as Integer returns Integer:
    Return proc create_hcl_parser from tokens
End Process

@Reasoning:
Snake-case public alias for parse_hcl_configuration. Same dispatcher-
naming convention as hcl_parser_create. The body delegates to the
canonical implementation.
@End Reasoning
Process called "hcl_parse_configuration" takes parser as Integer returns Integer:
    Return proc parse_hcl_configuration from parser
End Process
